OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm and
OL,6,Fsunny evening. Remaining dry overnight
OL,7,Fwith clear spells but some low cloud
OL,8,Fwill develop in the east. A warm night
OL,9,Fin the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FLow cloud in the east will
OL,12,Fsoon burn back to the coast, Otherwise
OL,13,Fit will be another dry and sunny day.
OL,14,FVery warm in the west.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,17,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine.
OL,18,FVery warm in the west with the best of
OL,19,Fthe sunshine, cloudier and cooler at
OL,20,Ftimes in the east.
